Nicky Spurgeon is an extremely accomplished con man who takes an amateur 
con artist, Jess, under his wing. Nicky and Jess become romantically 
involved, and with Nicky's profession of being a liar and a cheater for

together. They split, only to see each other three years later... And 
things get messy.
